                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">船号：</span>闽泉渔00123</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">来港目的：</span>卸货</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">靠泊泊位：</span>DF-A-01</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">进港时间：</span>2024-06-08 06:30</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">预计离港：</span>2024-06-10</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">船长：</span>王大海</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">船员人数：</span>12人</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">渔获物总量：</span>8,520 kg</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">登记人员：</span>港务员李平</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer"><button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" data-bs-dismiss="modal">关 闭</button><button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="printRecord()"><i class="bi bi-printer me-1"></i>打印单据</button></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
